OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FITV News Deputy Political Editor
OL,7,FAnushka Asthana talks us through the
OL,8,FChancellor's announcements and the
OL,9,Fscale of tax changes to come
OL,11,FIn a pivotal moment for the UK
OL,12,Feconomy, Chancellor Rachel Reeves has
OL,13,Funveiled a series of bold tax measures
OL,14,Faiming to keep borrowing under control
OL,15,Fand prevent a return to austerity.
OL,17,FAmong the headline aspects of
OL,18,FWednesday's Budget was a hike in how
OL,19,Fmuch employers will pay in national
OL,20,Finsurance contributions - up by 1.2
OL,21,Fpercentage points to 15%.
