OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FThe tax rises announced by Reeves
OL,7,Fappeared targeted generally at wealth,
OL,8,Frather than income. Increases in
OL,9,Fcapital gains tax and changes to
OL,10,Finheritance tax and stamp duty were
OL,11,Falso key features of her speech.
OL,13,FAddressing Parliament, Reeves promised
OL,14,Fnot to increase the headline taxes on
OL,15,Fthe pay cheques of "working people":
OL,16,Fnational insurance, VAT and income tax.
OL,18,FAfter entering office in July, the
OL,19,Fgovernment said it needed to fill a
OL,20,F#22 billion "black hole" in the public
OL,21,Ffinances.
