OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FReeves is said to have since
OL,7,Fidentified a far larger #40 billion
OL,8,Ffunding gap which she will seek to
OL,9,Fplug to protect key departments from
OL,10,Freal-terms cuts and put the economy on
OL,11,Fa firmer footing.
OL,13,FBut last week the Institute for Fiscal
OL,14,FStudies warned that up to #25 billion
OL,15,Fin tax rises would be needed to
OL,16,Ffulfill Reeves' promise of "no return
OL,17,Fto austerity".
OL,19,FHere, ITV News explains what tax
OL,20,Fmeasures were laid out in Wednesday's
OL,21,FBudget.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
