OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FEmployer National Insurance
OL,8,FReeves has announced a substantial
OL,9,Fincrease in Employer National
OL,10,FInsurance Contributions, raising the
OL,11,Frate of Employers' National Insurance
OL,12,Fby 1.2% to 15% from April 2025.
OL,14,FThe Secondary Threshold, the amount an
OL,15,Femployee has to earn before an
OL,16,Femployer has to start paying national
OL,17,Finsurance on each salary, is set to be
OL,18,Freduced from #9100 per year, to #5000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
