OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FEmployers currently pay 13.8% on
OL,7,Fearnings above #175 a week, or #9100 a
OL,8,Fyear per person, under Class 1 NI
OL,9,Fcontributions. It's deducted and set
OL,10,Faside for HMRC before wages are paid
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,FReeves said: "I do not take this
OL,14,Fdecision lightly. We are asking
OL,15,Fbusiness to contribute more."
