OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FHowever, the chancellor did put
OL,7,Fforward an exception for small
OL,8,Fbusinesses, increasing the Employment
OL,9,FAllowance, an initiative which allows
OL,10,Feligible employers to reduce their
OL,11,FNational Insurance liability.
OL,12,FEmployment Allowance will now go up
OL,13,Ffrom #5000 to #10,500.
OL,15,FSince the election, speculation has
OL,16,Fswirled around employer National
OL,17,FInsurance contributions being
OL,18,Fincreased.
