OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FThe key question was whether this
OL,7,Fbreaks Labour's manifesto promise not
OL,8,Fto raise taxes for "working people".
OL,10,FThe PM has suggested it does not, but
OL,11,Fbusiness groups say an increase in
OL,12,Femployer NI would be a "clear
OL,13,Fmanifesto breach", placing "an
OL,14,Fadditional strain on businesses".
OL,16,FThey argue a rise will impact working
OL,17,Fpeople as employers could restrict new
OL,18,Fhires, limit pay rises, scale back
OL,19,Fpension payments or even put up prices
OL,20,Ffor customers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
