OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FIncome tax thresholds
OL,8,FReeves has said she will not extend
OL,9,Fthe freeze on income tax thresholds,
OL,10,Fwhich are the income levels at which
OL,11,Fpeople start paying NI or income tax.
OL,13,FThese used to rise every year in line
OL,14,Fwith inflation but, the NI threshold
OL,15,Fand tax-free personal allowance are
OL,16,Fcurrently frozen at #12,570 until 2028.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
