OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FReeves announced on Wednesday that
OL,7,Ffrom the year 2028 to 2029, personal
OL,8,Ftax thresholds will be once again
OL,9,Fuprated in line with inflation once
OL,10,Fagain.
OL,12,F"Having considered the issue closely,
OL,13,FI have come to the conclusion that
OL,14,Fextending the threshold freeze would
OL,15,Fhurt working people. It would take
OL,16,Fmore money out of their payslips," the
OL,17,Fchancellor said.
