OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FCapital gains tax is paid by around
OL,7,F350,000 people, which is less than 1%
OL,8,Fof the population.
OL,10,FIt's the tax levied on any profit when
OL,11,Fsomeone sells an asset worth more than
OL,12,F#6,000 - like a second home, or shares.
OL,14,FThe CGT rate is 10% for profits above
OL,15,F#3,000, or 18% on profits from selling
OL,16,Fa residential property other than a
OL,17,Fmain home.
OL,19,FThe higher rate of CGT is 24% on
OL,20,Fresidential property and 20% on all
OL,21,Fother chargeable assets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
