OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FIn her Budget, the chancellor has
OL,7,Fincreased the lower rate of capital
OL,8,Fgains tax from 10% to 18%, and the
OL,9,Fhigher rate from 20% to 24%.
OL,11,FThe rates of capital gains tax on
OL,12,Fhomes and other residential properties
OL,13,Fwill be maintained at 18% and 24%.
OL,15,FCorporation tax
OL,17,FCorporation tax is paid by UK
OL,18,Fcompanies on the annual profits a
OL,19,Fcompany makes - the current main rate
OL,20,Fis 25%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
