OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FReeves confirmed she will cap
OL,7,Fcorporation tax at 25% for the rest of
OL,8,Fthe parliament, the lowest rate of the
OL,9,FG7 countries.
OL,11,FInheritance tax
OL,13,FInheritance tax is paid on someone's
OL,14,Festate when they die - it includes
OL,15,Ftheir property and other assets, but
OL,16,Fnot if the value is below #325,000.
OL,18,FIt's currently taxed at 40%, but only
OL,19,Fon the part of the estate above the
OL,20,Fthreshold.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
