OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FThe number of people who pay
OL,7,Finheritance tax is very small - last
OL,8,Fyear only 5% of estates were charged
OL,9,Fan inheritance tax bill, and there are
OL,10,Falso quite a lot of exemptions.
OL,12,FIn her Budget, Reeves announced she
OL,13,Fwould extend the freeze on inheritance
OL,14,Ftax thresholds introduced under the
OL,15,Fprevious governments, from 2028 for
OL,16,Ftwo further years, until 2030.
