OL,6,FThis means the first #325,000 of any
OL,7,Festate can still be inherited tax-
OL,8,Ffree, increasing to #500,000 if the
OL,9,Festate includes a residence passed on
OL,10,Fto direct descendants.
OL,12,FOn inheritance taxes applied to farms,
OL,13,Fthe chancellor announced agricultural
OL,14,Fproperty relief and business property
OL,15,Frelief will be reformed.
