OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FShe said that from April 2026, there
OL,7,Fwould continue to be no inheritance
OL,8,Ftax on the first #1 million of
OL,9,Fcombined business and agricultural
OL,10,Fassets. However, for assets over #1
OL,11,Fmillion, inheritance tax will apply
OL,12,Fwith 50% relief, at an effective rate
OL,13,Fof 20%.
OL,15,FFuel duty on standard petrol and
OL,16,Fdiesel is currently 52.95p per litre,
OL,17,Fafter the Conservatives cut it by 5p
OL,18,Fin 2022. It's expected to raise #24.7
OL,19,Fbillion in 2023-2024 according for the
OL,20,FOffice for Budget Responsibility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
