OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Reeves announced she
OL,7,Fwill freeze fuel duty next year, also
OL,8,Fmaintaining the Tories' 5p cut for
OL,9,Fanother year.
OL,11,F"There will be no higher taxes at the
OL,12,Fpetrol pumps next year," she said.
