OL,3,CNI and alcohol duty: What taxes did
OL,4,CReeves change in her Budget?
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the Conservative
OL,7,Fgovernment froze the rates of alcohol
OL,8,Fduty, a measure which was due to stay
OL,9,Fin place until February 2025.
OL,11,FReeves said rather than uprating
OL,12,Fproducts alcoholic drinks sold on
OL,13,Fdraught in line with inflation, she
OL,14,Fwill cut draught duty by 1.7%.
OL,16,FThis would amount to "a penny off a
OL,17,Fpint in the pub", the chancellor added.
